description:
In this week's episode of Star Players, House of the Dragon star Abubakar Salim doesn't want to think about the thousands of hours he's played of World of Warcraft. 

This week on Star Players, host Lucy James is joined by Abubakar Salim, game director of Tales of Kenzera: Zau, and actor best known for Raised By Wolves, House of the Dragon, and Ridley Scott's Napoleon. Abubakar walks us through his gaming journey from his earliest memories playing Golden Axe, to the thousands of hours he's played of World of Warcraft, to his favorite game of all time, Golden Sun.
title: House Of The Dragon Star Abubakar Salim Was ADDICTED To WoW
